because I know this is not where you're from

00:02:22.680 --> 00:02:24.000
originally.

00:02:24.000 --> 00:02:24.560
That's right.

00:02:24.560 --> 00:02:25.560
Yeah, yeah.

00:02:25.560 --> 00:02:27.400
I'm Ha-Joon Chang.

00:02:27.400 --> 00:02:30.680
I'm a professor at SOAS,

00:02:30.680 --> 00:02:32.880
University of London, at the moment.

