Actually, I went to university in Korea.

00:09:06.560 --> 00:09:06.920
Okay.

00:09:06.920 --> 00:09:07.480
In Seoul?

00:09:07.480 --> 00:09:07.920
Yeah.

00:09:07.920 --> 00:09:10.360
So we studied economics, and,

00:09:10.360 --> 00:09:12.000
yeah, some professors were different,

