but most of the professors were just

00:09:14.920 --> 00:09:18.640
teaching this equilibrium models, you know?

00:09:18.640 --> 00:09:20.800
The similar models to what I would have learned.

00:09:20.800 --> 00:09:21.200
Exactly.

00:09:21.600 --> 00:09:23.520
Mathematically less sophisticated,

00:09:23.560 --> 00:09:24.840
but the same idea.

00:09:24.840 --> 00:09:25.160
Yeah.

00:09:25.160 --> 00:09:25.480
Okay.

